data.description:
Discover an exceptional opportunity that's truly unheard of. Zoned R-12 this 4 bed (one non-conforming) 2 bath (one with a walk in tub) on nearly 1/2 acre in the heart of Coeur d'Alene boasts a 25x40 shop and a green house that could be up and running with a little love. This property holds remarkable potential for income generation. Whether you're an investor with an eye for possibilities or someone seeking a unique property to transform, this canvas is ready for your vision. With abundant offstreet parking and nestled in an unbeatable location, this property ensures quick and convenient commutes wherever you are headed. Moreover, everyone will love its
proximity to parks, hiking trails, frisbee golf, biking paths, tennis courts, and even pickleball. Don't hesitate to seize this extraordinary opportunity and unlock the potential that awaits.
